14 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
15 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 21 O.S. 2021, Section 852.1, is
16 amended to read as follows:
17 Section 852.1. A. A person who is the parent, guardian, or
18 person having custody or control over a child as defined in Section
19 1-1-105 of Title 10A of the Oklahoma Statutes, commits child
20 endangerment when the person:
21 1. Knowingly permits physical or sexual abuse of a child;
22 2. Knowingly permits a child to be present at a location where
23 a controlled dangerous substance is being manufactured or attempted
